@startuml
title Student Payment - State and Reversal Diagram
skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAF7
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam ArrowColor #9A8700

[*] --> pending : create charge
pending --> overdue : dueAt passed (presentation state)
pending --> paid : record collection
overdue --> paid : collect outstanding amount
pending --> cancelled : cancel unpaid obligation / reason
overdue --> cancelled : administrative cancellation / reason
paid --> reversed : create opposite movement / reason

cancelled --> [*]
reversed --> [*]

state reversed {
  state "Original remains paid" as Original
  state "New reversal row\namount = -original amount" as ReversalRow
  [*] --> Original
  Original --> ReversalRow
  ReversalRow --> [*]
}

note right of paid
Paid movements are immutable financial evidence.
They are corrected through a linked reversal,
never by deletion.
end note

note bottom of reversed
reversalOfId is unique and preserves
the complete accounting trace.
end note
@enduml
